<h1>Welcome to the Corridor!</h1>

<p>This website is your place to learn and share about the life of Michigan Avenue, a
commercial corridor that runs through Lansing and East Lansing, Michigan.  It's sponsored
by the Michigan Avenue Corridor Improvement Authority and Michigan State University.</p>

<h2>What can I do here?</h2>
<div id="goals_left">
	<div id="takeaction">
		<h3><%= link_to 'Improvement Ideas', articles_path %></h3>
		<p>Learn about proposed changes to the corridor and the New 
              Urbanism principles behind them, and suggest your own ideas.</p>
	</div><!-- End takeaction -->
   <div id="readnews">
		<h3><%= link_to 'Corridor News', :controller => 'news' %></h3>
		<p>Read about what's happening on the Corridor, with stories 
              from many different sources.</p>
	</div><!-- End readnews -->
   <div id="sharestories">
		<h3><%= link_to 'Share Your Stories', stories_path %></h3>
		<p>Share your stories of Michigan Avenue: the places and people 
              that turn a street into a community.</p>
   </div><!-- End sharestories -->
</div> <!-- End Goals Left -->

<div id="goals_right">
	<div id="mapit">
		<h3><%= link_to 'Map Opinions', maps_path %></h3>
		<p>It's just a straight line on most maps.  But it's much more
                  on ours. Share points of interest.</p>
	</div><!-- End mapit -->
	<div id="learnabout">
		<h3><%= link_to 'About the Corridor', :controller => "site", :action => "mac" %></h3>
		<p>See a list of events and activities happening on and around
                  the Corridor, and add your own.</p>
	</div><!-- End learnabout -->
	<div id="aboutsite">
		<h3> <%= link_to 'About This Site', :controller => "site", :action => "about" %> </h3>
		<p>Learn more about the group behind this site, and link to our 
              favorite websites for the Michigan Avenue Corridor.</p>
	</div><!-- End aboutsite -->
</div> <!-- End Goals Right -->
